Constructor Detail

MessageHeader.HeaderData

public MessageHeader.HeaderData(String recipient,
                                long messageId,
                                Long nonReplayableId,
                                boolean renewable,
                                boolean handshake,
                                MessageCapabilities capabilities,
                                Set<KeyRequestData> keyRequestData,
                                KeyResponseData keyResponseData,
                                UserAuthenticationData userAuthData,
                                UserIdToken userIdToken,
                                Set<ServiceToken> serviceTokens)
Parameters:
recipient - the message recipient's entity identity. May be null.
messageId - the message ID.
nonReplayableId - the message's non-replayable ID. May be null.
renewable - the message's renewable flag.
handshake - the message's handshake flag.
capabilities - the sender's message capabilities.
keyRequestData - session key request data. May be null or empty.
keyResponseData - session key response data. May be null.
userAuthData - the user authentication data. May be null if a user ID token is provided or there is no user authentication for this message.
userIdToken - the user ID token. May be null if user authentication data is provided or there is no user authentication for this message.
serviceTokens - the service tokens. May be null or empty.
